  "texts": [
    "Use Cases: All participants used at least one offthe-shelf AI tool created by big tech companies such as Google, OpenAI, and Microsoft.",
    "P4, P7, P8, and P10 also used internally created AI-based software.",
    "The most frequently mentioned AI usage scenarios were for processing and analyzing data (P2, P3, P10, P11) and chatbots (P1, P5, P6, P9).",
    "Furthermore, AI was used to write code (P2, P7, P8), to automate processes (P4, P11), to recognize patterns (P8), as a recommendation algorithm (P6), to forecast (P10), to build custom GenAI tooling (P7), and to translate (P5) and summarize text (P9).",
    "Founder P2 primarily used AI to process data: \"What we are looking into more and more is to let AI do our analysis for us."
  ],
